        Construct a BloodPressureRecord object.
        Parameters:
        rawRxCmdList - TaiDoc Bus raw command array list that receive from meter
        measureTime - Measure Time
        user - PCLinkLibraryEnum.User
        systolicValue - Systolic Value
        diastolicValue - Diastolic Value
        mapValue - MAP Value
        pulseValue - Pulse Value
        arrhy - Is Arrhythmia or not, true:Arrhythmia , false:Normal
        transmitted - The reading has been transmitted or not (支援sim卡的meter，若資料有透過sim卡上傳後，會註記為true)
        avg - true:Average measurement reading, false:Single measurement reading
        eve - true:Evening time measurement, false:Day time measurement
